* Iron Raptor shook her head and walked over to Prowl, looking down at him 
and waiting for the SBM to ware off now that she had removed hers.
She looked back at the group, slightly surprised when Mantle came forward.
So...there was another Maximals gestalt, how nice. It was good to have more 
heavy hitters on the team.
But what they wanted to know...the answer probably wasn't what they wanted 
to hear.
Iron Raptor bent down to take Prowl's head in her arms, hoping that he 
didn't wake up and suddenly bite her arm off.*

" Um...I hate to tell you this but Striker and his group don't exist 
anymore."

* She heaved, trying to lift Prowls head.*

" This..." she gestured to Prowl. " This is the last of his crew and he was 
attacking me but nothing I couldn't have stopped."
